    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Full Matrix Multiplication\n",
        "\n",
        "We compute:\n",
        "\n",
        "$$\n",
        "\\begin{align}\n",
        "\\tilde{H} = XW_{xh} + HW_{hh}\n",
        "\\end{align}\n",
        "$$\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "#### Compute $XW_{xh}$\n",
        "\n",
        "$$\n",
        "\\begin{align}\n",
        "X =\n",
        "\\begin{bmatrix}\n",
        "-0.5881 \\\\\n",
        "-1.7512 \\\\\n",
        "-0.4868\n",
        "\\end{bmatrix},\n",
        "\\quad\n",
        "W_{xh} =\n",
        "\\begin{bmatrix}\n",
        "0.3575 & -0.4725 & 0.7883 & -1.0517\n",
        "\\end{bmatrix}\n",
        "\\end{align}\n",
        "$$\n",
        "\n",
        "$$\n",
        "\\begin{align}\n",
        "XW_{xh} =\n",
        "\\begin{bmatrix}\n",
        "-0.5881 \\cdot 0.3575 &\n",
        "-0.5881 \\cdot (-0.4725) &\n",
        "-0.5881 \\cdot 0.7883 &\n",
        "-0.5881 \\cdot (-1.0517)\n",
        "\\\\[6pt]\n",
        "-1.7512 \\cdot 0.3575 &\n",
        "-1.7512 \\cdot (-0.4725) &\n",
        "-1.7512 \\cdot 0.7883 &\n",
        "-1.7512 \\cdot (-1.0517)\n",
        "\\\\[6pt]\n",
        "-0.4868 \\cdot 0.3575 &\n",
        "-0.4868 \\cdot (-0.4725) &\n",
        "-0.4868 \\cdot 0.7883 &\n",
        "-0.4868 \\cdot (-1.0517)\n",
        "\\end{bmatrix}\n",
        "\\end{align}\n",
        "$$\n",
        "\n",
        "Numerically:\n",
        "\n",
        "$$\n",
        "\\begin{align}\n",
        "XW_{xh} \\approx\n",
        "\\begin{bmatrix}\n",
        "-0.2102 & 0.2779 & -0.4637 & 0.6183 \\\\\n",
        "-0.6261 & 0.8270 & -1.3803 & 1.8410 \\\\\n",
        "-0.1740 & 0.2300 & -0.3837 & 0.5120\n",
        "\\end{bmatrix}\n",
        "\\end{align}\n",
        "$$\n",
        "\n",
        "#### Compute $HW_{hh}$\n",
        "\n",
        "$$\n",
        "\\begin{align}\n",
        "H =\n",
        "\\begin{bmatrix}\n",
        "0.5329 & -0.9700 & -0.8252 & -0.1636 \\\\\n",
        "0.9559 & -0.4783 & -1.6516 & 0.3654 \\\\\n",
        "0.1092 & -0.0745 & -1.5449 & -0.9735\n",
        "\\end{bmatrix}\n",
        "\\end{align}\n",
        "$$\n",
        "\n",
        "$$\n",
        "\\begin{align}\n",
        "W_{hh} =\n",
        "\\begin{bmatrix}\n",
        "1.2696 & -0.7332 & 0.5251 & 0.9043 \\\\\n",
        "-0.0312 & -1.9849 & 0.7119 & 0.7166 \\\\\n",
        "0.9789 & -0.9468 & 1.0339 & 0.0266 \\\\\n",
        "-0.6172 & 0.3988 & 0.0310 & -0.5180\n",
        "\\end{bmatrix}\n",
        "\\end{align}\n",
        "$$\n",
        "\n",
        "Let’s compute the **first row** explicitly (students love this):\n",
        "\n",
        "#### First row, first column:\n",
        "\n",
        "$$\n",
        "\\begin{align}\n",
        "0.5329(1.2696) +\n",
        "(-0.9700)(-0.0312) +\n",
        "(-0.8252)(0.9789) +\n",
        "(-0.1636)(-0.6172)\n",
        "\\end{align}\n",
        "$$\n",
        "\n",
        "$$\n",
        "\\begin{align}\n",
        "= 0.6767 + 0.0303 - 0.8077 + 0.1009 = 0.0002\n",
        "\\end{align}\n",
        "$$\n",
        "\n",
        "We’ll keep the full matrix:\n",
        "\n",
        "$$\n",
        "\\begin{align}\n",
        "HW_{hh} \\approx\n",
        "\\begin{bmatrix}\n",
        "0.0000 & 2.2507 & -1.2688 & -0.1502 \\\\\n",
        "-0.6136 & 1.9585 & -1.5350 & 0.2892 \\\\\n",
        "-0.7704 & 1.1424 & -1.6232 & 0.5084\n",
        "\\end{bmatrix}\n",
        "\\end{align}\n",
        "$$\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "#### Add Them\n",
        "\n",
        "$$\n",
        "\\begin{align}\n",
        "\\tilde{H} = XW_{xh} + HW_{hh}\n",
        "\\end{align}\n",
        "$$\n",
        "\n",
        "$$\n",
        "\\begin{align}\n",
        "\\tilde{H} \\approx\n",
        "\\begin{bmatrix}\n",
        "-0.2102 & 2.5286 & -1.7325 & 0.4681 \\\\\n",
        "-1.2397 & 2.7855 & -2.9153 & 2.1302 \\\\\n",
        "-0.9444 & 1.3724 & -2.0069 & 1.0204\n",
        "\\end{bmatrix}\n",
        "\\end{align}\n",
        "$$\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "Now we concatenate the matrices `X` and `H`\n",
        "along columns (axis 1),\n",
        "and the matrices\n",
        "`W_xh` and `W_hh` along rows (axis 0).\n",
        "These two concatenations\n",
        "result in\n",
        "matrices of shape (3, 5)\n",
        "and of shape (5, 4), respectively.\n",
        "Multiplying these two concatenated matrices,\n",
        "we obtain the same output matrix of shape (3, 4)\n",
        "as above."
      ],
