        "### Concatenated input:\n",
        "\n",
        "$$\n",
        "\\begin{align}\n",
        "XH = [\\,X \\;\\; H\\,] \\in \\mathbb{R}^{B \\times (d_x + d_h)}\n",
        "\\end{align}\n",
        "$$\n",
        "\n",
        "### Concatenated weights:\n",
        "\n",
        "$$\n",
        "\\begin{align}\n",
        "W =\n",
        "\\begin{bmatrix}\n",
        "W_{xh} \\\\\n",
        "W_{hh}\n",
        "\\end{bmatrix}\n",
